healthcheck 0.1.0
Andrew White <aeewhite@gmail.com>
Emulate kubernetes health check for testing purposes

USAGE:
    healthcheck [OPTIONS] <url>

FLAGS:
    -h, --help       Prints help information
    -V, --version    Prints version information

OPTIONS:
    -d, --delay <delay>                   Delay between health check calls [default: 15]
    -f, --failure-threshold <failures>    Failures before marking service as unhealthy [default: 3]
    -t, --timeout <timeout>               Request timeout for health check [default: 10]

ARGS:
    <url>    The URL to check
